<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회사 인트라넷 게시판</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .board-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .board-header h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .board-header .add-post {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .board-header .add-post:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        .board-list {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .board-list li {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .board-list li:hover {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .board-list .title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

        .board-list .date {
            color: #888;
        }

        .board-list .actions {
            color: #4CAF50;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .board-list .actions:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    양정인력개발센터 인트라넷 게시판
</header>

<div class="container">
    <div class="board-header">
        <h2>게시글 목록</h2>
        <button class="add-post" onclick="window.location.href='/board/new'">글쓰기</button>
    </div>

    <ol class="board-list">
    {{#boards}}
        <li>
            <a href="/board/{{id}}">
                <div class="title">게시물번호 : {{id}}번</div>
                <div class="title">{{title}}</div>
                <div class="date">{{createDate}}</div>
            </a>
        </li>
    {{/boards}}
    </ol>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2025 양정인력개발센터 - 모든 권리 보유
</footer>

</body>
</html>
